data.description: Welcome to this amazing opportunity to own in the city of Los Angeles! This home features a fully remodeled 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, with a long drive way to fit many cars and a HUGE back yard with potential to build an ADU or to enjoy family gatherings, parties and play ground for the kids! Property is located near schools, and easy FWY access, This home is perfect for a first time home buyer or existing buyers!!  Come check out this amazing investment opportunity as it offers many more features you have to come see for yourself!! AMAZING opportunity to call this your home!!
